Other than that, it's great to type on and looks lovely.

text: The MX Keys Mini is a lovely keyboard. I'm very happy with mine. My only criticism is Logitech's decision to go for non-standard F-keys. Not having the normal shortcuts for screen brightness, launchpad, and mission control is a little annoying. You can remap the F-keys in Logitech Options, but standard Mac F-keys would've been better. Other than that, it's great to type on and looks lovely.
